                <note rend="inline" type="source">832.51/1735: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Caffery</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-03-05T21:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 5, 1940—9 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>54. Discussions still continue with Council but hope for favorable result
                    tomorrow. Please try to hold matters open. Possibly Aranha <pb facs="0604"
                        n="592" xml:id="pg_592"/> could obtain authority to make offer immediately
                    upon receiving proposed assurances.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
